12. Explain fully the circumstances of all payments, including the terms of any oral agreement or understanding pursuant to which they were made.
The payments made in April were for the expenses incurred at the New York New England Apprentice
Conference held 4/18-20, 2008 in New York City. The payment made in June and the credit card
payment in July were for expenses incurred at the National Apprentice Conference held in Hershey, PA
6/22-28, 2008. Other reimbursements were for expenses paid by Mr. Glavey for training classes. All
expenses were incurred for expenses of the Training Fund.
